  "title": "Crew Leader",
  "description": "<h1><strong>🥐 Passion Is Our Main Ingredient🥐</strong></h1><p><strong>Baker & Cook Singapore </strong>- Singapore’s only true artisan bakery & foodstore is hiring!</p><h3>💰 <strong>** Attractive Sign-on Bonus**</strong>💰</h3><p>✅ Singaporean* | Singapore PR* | PLOC</p><p>✅ 6-days rostered work week</p><p>**Attractive Sign-on Bonus**</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>🍕 Outlets: Asian Civilizations Museum </strong>| <strong>Café Carrera by Baker & Cook (Guoco Midtown) | Café Carrera by Baker & Cook (Jewel) | Chip Bee Garden | Dairy Farm | Dempsey | Eng Kong Park | Hillcrest | Namly Place | South Bouna Vista | Serangoon Garden | Swan Lake | Sunset Way</strong></p><p><br /><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Ensuring excellent guest experience through providing of warm and genuine service</li><li>Take, prepare and serve food & drinks and operate cash register</li><li>Ensure product items are well stocked and display cases are attractive and clean</li><li>Maintain a high standard of cleanliness in and around workstation and strictly abide with health/sanitation regulations</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties base on operational needs</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Passionate about service and people</li><li>At least GCE “N” level or its equivalent</li><li>Preferably 1 year working experience in F&B – cafes/ restaurants/ similar capacity</li><li>Those with no experience are welcome to apply</li><li>Good team player and self-motivated</li><li>6 days work week and able to work on weekends/public holiday</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><ul><li>Medical + dental benefits</li><li>Birthday vouchers</li><li>Staff discounts across brands</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested party may apply via https://forms.gle/G1q4e4nDrfW1yDmL7</p><p>** T&C applies</p>",
